metadata.name: Dream #1
metadata.description: Dream Society is a collection of Dreamers roaming the Ethereum blockchain. Our team has worked meticulously with our artists from DreamWorks, Marvel & Bob's Burgers to curate an imaginative and diverse collection that represents all the different types of Dreamers within our community. Dreams have brought life to our characters which have their own unique quirks and origin stories reflected in their backgrounds and character-specific traits such as mushroom caps, mounts, and pets.
